I"<p><strong>Medium humanoid (kuo-toa), neutral evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 13 (natural armor, shield)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 18 (4d8)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft., swim 30 ft.</p>

